{"tid":2289430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"威斯康星州選舉部門：若特朗普陣營要求重點選票 須繳付近800萬美元費用","createTime":"2020-11-17T08:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T11:34:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":18,"dislike":138,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4f905174445be5225443dba07ebbff1b820dcb","tid":2289430,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨人撤回4州選舉訴訟 未有解釋原因<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨人撤回在4個州挑戰大選點票的訴訟，分別是密歇根、佐治亞、賓夕法尼亞及威斯康星州，未有交代原因。<br />\n<br />\n訴訟當初由共和黨人以選民身分提出，並非特朗普陣營人士，亦非共和黨官員。這4個州未正式完成點票，主流傳媒都推算民主黨的拜登勝出。<br />\n<br />\n另外，威斯康星州選舉部門表示，若特朗普陣營要求重點選票，必須繳付近800萬美元的費用。傳媒推算拜登在這個州，領先特朗普2萬票。<br />\n<br />\n佐治亞州發現近2600張未點的選票，官員解釋有工作人員處理失當。傳媒推算特朗普能取得當中800票，但不足以扭轉敗局，因為拜登領先超過1萬4千票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560444-20201117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560444-20201117.htm&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM43XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=a08a917c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560444-20201117.htm&h=48caf7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560444-20201117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2b28d93d1532ced5bfe7d5e2c43caee59b624943","tid":2289430,"uid":112846,"like":75,"dislike":7,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"當撈侵點會冇錢?"},{"pid":"16b364daa4c292f1d61e18f09d7a1de105657d46","tid":2289430,"uid":14918,"like":165,"dislike":7,"score":158,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"證明到你出錯, 咁你就有責任重點架啦<br />\n自己出錯仲要收錢?"},{"pid":"08efec7e2ffe462c6a9cc5010d8a2a9e5d80f834","tid":2289430,"uid":138964,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"我地捐俾trump 會唔會告 trump 洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663107a392e035ced760710c5f157e1068ed258a","tid":2289430,"uid":32782,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"